{"tid":2388584,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人記得舒夫真高當年幾勁?","createTime":"2021-01-31T08:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T15:30:54.000Z","uid":237459,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"087f7c093aeaa4afb3edd21058fbd6a9f10d069e","tid":2388584,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:54:08.000Z","msg":"亞姐冠軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n達蓮娜&middot;舒夫真高（俄語：Дарына Шевченко），哈薩克烏克蘭族人。2006年以16歲之齡成為歷來最年輕的亞洲小姐競選冠軍（8號）、完美體態大獎得主、最佳儀態風度小姐。同時是香港選美史上唯一一位非華裔的選美冠軍，與亞洲電視約滿後返回哈薩克。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hyqRTei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhyqRTei.jpg&h=21c9a39c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee6b86949b7c9604cbecd6c17a17d228873be213","tid":2388584,"uid":158755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"06年拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e6e13ae58b24754bc949ac78a1513bc1146d97","tid":2388584,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee6b86949b7c9604cbecd6c17a17d228873be213","tid":2388584,"uid":158755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"06年拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:11:47.000Z","msg":"30歲仲可以一戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f51e8cf4f03a403a58b5ad88e3e4a81dd971baf","tid":2388584,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:12:31.000Z","msg":"唔係踢波果個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5469b10e76a2b6c986a822837182ef6116488dd2","tid":2388584,"uid":3363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:21: